OWNERSHIP & PROVENANCE
----------------------
This skill carries an ownership mark in several places so a copy can be traced back
to its author:

  * Visible attribution: this NOTICE, plus a copyright header in the core helper files.
  * Machine-checkable mark: helpers/_common.py OWNER_MARK / OWNER_FINGERPRINT (also a
    zero-width provenance canary, OWNER_CANARY). helpers/preflight.py verifies the mark
    is present and unaltered on every run.
  * Tamper-evidence: assets/integrity.json records the SHA-256 of the marked files;
    helpers/preflight.py flags any change. (Honest limit: this DETECTS tampering; a
    determined editor can re-run helpers/make_integrity.py to re-bless an edited copy.
    Nothing in a plain-text skill can be made literally unremovable.)
